    <h1>YouTube Monetization But No Views: Monetized Channels Par Traffic Zero Kyun Hota Hai? (Complete Guide)</h1>

    <p><strong>Meta Description:</strong> YouTube channel monetized hai lekin views down ho gaye hain? Is detailed guide mein janiye algorithm ki working, CTR, Audience retention, aur dead channel ko grow karne ka mukammal 30-day roadmap.</p>

